By default terraform stores the state files on the default backend called local(as a local file on the disk)

terraform.tfstate -> is the the local terraform statefiles



In a real time environment, the ideal archetecture is,

-> terraform scripts are stored in a git repo
-> statefiles are stored in central backend

some popular backends are,

    s3,
    Consul
    Azurerm
    Kubernetes
    HTTP
    ETCD etc..

    

